title: Doctor Doom And The Masters of Evil 01-04 (2009|Minutemen+)
description:
This All Ages comic takes place in the Marvel Adventures universe and is written by Paul Tobin with art from Patrick Scherberger. Promotional info - "You've gotta ask yourself: If Doctor Doom's the most evil guy ever, how much more evil's it gonna get when he puts a whole TEAM of VILLAINS to work? It's the series where the bad guys get their say, and the Sinister Six are saying they aren't sinister enough! So, what's the solution? How about Kraven stealing a vibranium staff from the Louvre? Sweet! And how about Electro designs a new suit to better channel his powers? Great idea! And how about ramping up Mysterio's powers by breaking into Stark Industries to steal a miniaturized super-component, battling both Iron Man and Dr. Strange in the process?"

This fills a request from KAT. These scans are all by Minutemen scanners, specifically MM-DTs and MM-Hawaiian Punch. Thanks for them for their efforts, please seed and enjoy!
